Certainly, here are some examples of how to use the word "nijedna" in Serbian with translations in English:

1. Nijedna *žena* ne voli da bude ignorisana. (No woman likes to be ignored.)
2. *Nijedna* knjiga nije bila zanimljiva kao ova. (No book was as interesting as this one.)
3. U ovoj sobi nema *nijedne* stolice. (There isn't a single chair in this room.)
4. *Nijedna* od nas ne zna kako to da uradi. (None of us knows how to do it.)
5. Ona neće dati *nijedan* dinar za to. (She won't give a single dinar for that.)
6. *Nijedan* od tih odgovora nije bio tačan. (None of those answers were correct.)
7. *Nijedna* reč nije bila izgovorena tokom celog sastanka. (Not a single word was spoken during the entire meeting.)
8. Ja *nijednu* sekundu nisam spavao sinoć. (I didn't sleep a single second last night.)
9. *Nijedna* boja ne može da zameni crnu. (No color can replace black.)
10. On nije pitao *nijedno* pitanje tokom časa. (He didn't ask a single question during class.)